hopobject.body: An envelope xyzal allergy 24 hour Wainwright's night is over after five innings, and John Axford comes in from the St. Louis bullpen. Only three of the five runs against Wainwright are earned, and having thrown 95 pitches, he looks like a good bet to return on three days' rest in Game 4, which in turn would line him up for a Game 7 start, also on three days' rest. Axford strikes out Bogaerts, Drew and Ross in a breeze of an inning.
